      <abstract>
        <div>
          <p>This is the abstract text. It describes the motivation, method, and main findings of the sample paper. The work introduces a new framework for processing academic PDFs and extracting structured metadata using a combination of statistical and machine-learning techniques.</p>
          <p>The proposed approach achieves state-of-the-art results on three benchmark datasets while remaining computationally efficient. We also perform an extensive ablation study to identify the contribution of each component.</p>
        </div>
      </abstract>
